subproject.corporate outcome: Development plans and programmes integrate environmentally sustainable solutions in a manner that promotes poverty reduction, MDG achievement and low-emission climate-resilient development
subproject.description:
The Project aims at;

1- Assessment report to  provide an overview of Jeddah environmental situation.
2- Project document including work plan and budget in preparation for the Environmental Master Plan .
3- Production of Jeddah EMP PD
subproject.title: Jeddah Environmental Master Pl
